  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Transport use during the coronavirus (COVID-19) pandemic
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  

  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">To monitor the use of the transport system during the coronavirus (COVID-19) pandemic. DfT provides statistics on transport use by mode.</p>

  </div>
</div>

