    <h2 class="title"><a href="/government/publications/transport-use-during-the-coronavirus-covid-19-pandemic/covid-19-transport-data-methodology-note">COVID-19 transport data: methodology note</a></h2>
    <p class="metadata">
        <span class="type">HTML</span>
